lead_paragraph: Ignacio Piatti scored in the 73rd minute and Montreal Impact beat Toronto FC 1-0 on Saturday night to end the Reds' unbeaten streak at seven games.

headline.print_headline: Impact Wins 1-0, Ends Toronto's Unbeaten Streak at 7 Games
